Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 845.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colossal Titan and the Armored Titan appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, the walls were shattered, along with the illusory peace of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind abandoned Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They lost a fifth of their population, and a third of their territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as human activity was pushed back to Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in Year 850,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Colossal Titan once again appeared out of nowhere and broke the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and humanity allowed the Titans to advance further still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers fell one after another facing down the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, despite having been eaten by a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly emerged from a mysterious Titan's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot Pixis, the Commander-in-Chief of the defense of the southern territories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,set eyes on Eren's power to turn into a Titan in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and set a certain operation in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He will transform into a Titan, pick up that giant boulder near the front gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,carry it to the breach in the wall, and block off the hole with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When this plan succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be the first time we've ever reconquered land from the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It will mean mankind has finally managed an attack on the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the moment the operation \Ncommenced, it appeared to have failed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to lure most of the Titans to this distant corner of the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but despite avoiding combat as much as possible, we lost a fifth of our men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers didn't just die on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent them to their deaths on my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a critical point in mankind's survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means mankind will live on, I \Ndon't mind being called a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Ackerman! Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, don't you recognize me? I'm Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must block the hole with that boulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious from the start that no secret weapon existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! You're human! You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge, Ackerman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a stupid Titan like all the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad leader Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Two approaching from ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One 10-meter and one 6-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Another's coming from behind! It's a 12-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian, we gotta pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat ain't gonna block no gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We've got no choice but to leave him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Red signal flare from the elite team confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A serious problem has interfered with the blocking operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My comrades died in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all a waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they... fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Armin! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis, we should fall back to defending the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you approve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Order the elite team to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep luring the Titans to the corner of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the elite team, they have the authority to act as they see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't merely just skilled soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the elite among the elite that I entrusted with the future of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up so easily would be unforgiveable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow our comrades' deaths to be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We must struggle to our very last breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in command!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian, it's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan was dubious at best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth giving it a try,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've already tried it, with no success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! We're going up the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Calm down, Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rico, take down the 12-meter class coming from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitabi's squad and mine will handle the two in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one in command here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and listen to my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave Jaeger defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're changing our objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Jaeger can be retrieved, we'll protect him from the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He represents a precious possibility for mankind. We can't just abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike us, he can't be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds have already died for that hulking failure of a human weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you want to recover him, just for us to go through all that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! No matter how many die, we must try again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What happened to Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Armin's headed there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think... they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You {\i1}think{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They'll be fine! I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eren will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't help but think it's pointless to \Ngather the Titans in the corner of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fighting the Titans always becomes a battle of attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We can't let our soldiers perish at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So those who already died, they perished in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is bound to turn into an all-out war sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We must preserve our forces as much as possible until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Keeping our casualties to the minimum is only natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I am right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then let's try not to become casualties ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian, are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How else can mankind win against the Titans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Rico! What other way is there to get through this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we win against the Titans without more people dying, while staying humans ourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't know a way to defeat the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this is all we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For that messed-up human weapon's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we must risk our lives and give it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pitiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will you do? This is the only way we can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as much struggle as we can manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will follow the plan. I think what you're saying is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But while I struggle, I'll show them just how dreadful humans can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to die a dog's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the 12-meter class behind us for me and my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. The two ahead of us are ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, squad leader Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman, you shouldn't thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost shat myself because I had no clue what you were about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Move ahead on your own to execute the original plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your abilities are best utilized that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? His wounds aren't regenerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because of the damage he suffered before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What effects did that have on Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there any guarantee he can return to his normal form again at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should stop. It's not something I can figure out by thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I must do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren! Mikasa! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I sitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What day is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I'm at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I need sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Eren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? We mustn't let the Titans leave this corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus only on that goal, and lure them close enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadets will form groups of three and run on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're under the Wall, climb up it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If by some minuscule chance any \NTitans stray away, we'll crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Minuscule chance? I'd say it's more likely than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we free to act as we see fit in the case of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can sort it out that way, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirstein squad, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! Behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A 13-meter class is heading for Jaeger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,More Titans are coming in through the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like four 10-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman, handle the one behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them reach Jaeger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though they're the elite,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just two squads can't handle four at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no... Why are there so many Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are hardly any humans around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me... They're drawn to Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! What happened to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren can't control that Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't respond even when I tried talking to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in anyone else trying either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave Eren behind, so everyone's fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this many Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we're bound to get wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From the back of the head to the nape of the neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One meter vertically. Ten centimeters horizontally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Eren out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! Protect us from the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren came out of the Titan's weak point before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be related to the mystery of the Titan's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I avoid the middle, it won't be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just going to hurt a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! Right now, do what you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, there are lives you can save!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Eren to me and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come out of there, we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let a mere Titan body control you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out of that lump of flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get out of here? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren! Come out! Hurry! Eren! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to avenging your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to exterminate all the Titans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hate those bastards for killing your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Wake up, please! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here, we'll be killed by the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will end right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you're making no sense, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Why should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Join the Recon Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'd better move on our own now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman reporting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join Mitabi's squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've had enough of people dying on my account!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, it just {\i1}had{\i0} to break right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why isn't he using his 3D Maneuver Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sort this out myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Now I'm holding other people back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this really work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we going to explore the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Far, far beyond these walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To the burning water and the land of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To the snowfields of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To that world my parents were always hoping to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd forgotten about it, but you'd just stopped bringing it up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because you didn't want me to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you knew hell was raging outside the walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we might end up dying horrible deaths like my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ever want to see the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:22:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask? Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was born to {\i1}this{\i0} world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Run. Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:24:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the battlefield, where many words echo and many lives end,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren gives hope to humanity as he heads for the gate.
