Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.85,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ignore those pigs who ridicule you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.65,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}for having the will to step over dead bodies and move on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.45,0:02:40.37,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Our complacence as livestock strengthens this false reality
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.09,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}We're as free as starving wolves!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.93,0:02:48.49,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Channel the humiliation of imprisonment into your arrows and begin the resistance
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.21,0:02:53.71,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Far beyond the confining walls, you'll slay your prey!
